title: 2014 LET Access Series
text:
The 2014 LET Access Series was a series of professional women's <a href="golf">golf</a> tournaments held from May through October 2014 across Europe. The <a href="LET%20Access%20Series">LET Access Series</a> is the second-tier women's professional golf tour in Europe and is the official developmental tour of the <a href="Ladies%20European%20Tour">Ladies European Tour</a>.
Tournament results.
The table below shows the 2014 schedule. The numbers in brackets after the winners' names show the number of career wins they had on the LET Access Series up to and including that event.
Order of Merit rankings.
The top five players on the LETAS Order of Merit earn LET membership for the <a href="Ladies%20European%20Tour">Ladies European Tour</a>. Players finishing in positions 6–20 get to skip the first stage of the <a href="Qualifying%20School">qualifying event</a> and automatically progress to the final stage of the <a href="Qualifying%20School">Lalla Aicha Tour School</a>.
